resources.string: Morphosis is the annual technical festival organized by the Technical Society of NIT Mizoram.It is basically a techno-management festival that is organized every year with a sincere motive to inculcate the technical and managerial skills in the very nature of the participants.We are here with a plethora of indulging and needless to say, super exulting events that not only provide an excellent system of support to the participants but also provide them a distinguished platform to carve out the niche in their field of interest.
